Hello and welcome to your confessional channel! This is where you should dump all your thoughts about the game or anything else you want to talk about. You may also receive questions from hosts and spectators alike throughout the season. Please answer those promptly and have fun with them as well. This is a place you should be using to explain your thoughts on the game and reactions to the events unfolding around you. We want to see your journey progress throughout the season. Only our Hungry Spectators can see this as the season goes, they are all verified and trusted people, so no need to worry about any sort of leaks. Please make the most of your confessionals as it adds to the fun of the game! Spectators love reading these so use them as frequently as you would like. Do not complete challenges, submit votes, use commands, or say anything in here you wouldn't want the other players to see after the season, as this will all be public. To start you off good on these confessionals, please answer these basic starter questions! 1 - Tell us about yourself and your life! 2 - What are your first reactions about the game that lies ahead? 3 - How do you plan on playing this season to become the sole survivor? Good luck and have fun!
